title: Jumping GODZILLA CARS Across GTA 5! (Impossible)
author: Checkpoint
description:
Today, Steve is stealing Godzilla supercars to jump across the entire GTA 5 Dimension map! This stunt was nearly impossible, but with G.U.I.D.O on the line, we have to complete it! Can Steve from Checkpoint use the King Kong, Godzilla, Mecha Godzilla and Ghidorah god powers to stunt jump across the GTA 5 map to save G.U.I.D.O from Mesa?
